Package: GeoLight 
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Light Based Geolocator Data
Version: 3.0.0
Author: Simeon Lisovski, Simon Wotherspoon, Michael Sumner, Silke Bauer, Tamara Emmenegger, Paul Ritter
Maintainer: Simeon Lisovski <simeon.lisovski@gmail.com>
Description: Provides basic functions for global
    positioning based on light intensity measurements over time.
    Positioning process includes the determination of sun events, a
    discrimination of residency and movement periods, the
    calibration of period-specific data and, finally, the
    calculation of positions.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    changepoint,
    fields,
    MASS,
    rnaturalearth,
    terra,
    maps,
    ggplot2,
    sf,
    patchwork,
    dplyr
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
NeedsCompilation: no
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
